text: Rencunius is a genus of adapiform primate that lived in Asia during the late middle Eocene. It includes the species Rencunius zhoui. ==References== ===Literature cited=== * Category:Prehistoric strepsirrhines Category:Eocene mammals of Asia Category:Fossil taxa described in 1994 Category:Eocene primates †Rencunius Category:Prehistoric primate genera
